Markmade - Copyright (C) 2025 by Vivek Martin

Markmade is a plugin for Obsidian (www.obsidian.md) that lets users create raster graphics and embed them in markdown files. It is intended as a helpful tool, but is provided with no warranty of any kind.

Terms & Conditions:

Markmade is free to use for all purposes. This plugin is licensed for personal, commercial, government, educational, and non-profit use. It is a non-exclusive, non-transferable license, and the plugin is not sold.

If you'd like to support ongoing maintenance and future improvements of the plugin, your donation would be greatly appreciated.

